      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SECRET BANDIT (1) had been racing well with a Grade 4 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Wentworth Park. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. DENNIS KEEPING (3) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Wentworth Park following on from a second place finish (29.64) there the start prior. The form out of his last race has been franked. Likely to play a prominent role. DANGEROUS WHEELS (2) was out of in the placings when fourth last time but three runs back posted a handy 29.89 win over 520m at Wentworth Park. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. BACK TOMORROW (5) has merit but will need to be at her best to take this out.",
